  come up to Allentown.

04:23.264 --> 04:24.463
I wish I could.

04:24.565 --> 04:26.732
I mean, for good.

04:26.834 --> 04:28.500
Really?
 Okay, well, what did Mom say?

04:28.602 --> 04:30.135
 Did Mom say anything about it?

04:30.237 --> 04:32.137
Hey, Mom!
    C'mere!

04:32.239 --> 04:34.006
What?

04:34.108 --> 04:35.474
