04:38.846 --> 04:40.078
Is that so?

04:40.180 --> 04:41.913
Hi, Mom, I was--
  I was just talking to--

04:42.016 --> 04:43.282
Now, now.

04:43.384 --> 04:46.151
 The whole reason why you moved
in with Grandma was to help her.

04:46.253 --> 04:48.553
      She's countin' on ya.

04:48.656 --> 04:52.291
      You don't want to let
      her down now, do you?

04:52.393 --> 04:54.359
No, but...
   Mom, I--

04:54.461 --> 04:57.663
You be good now.

05:02.102 --> 05:05.170
I'll work on her.

05:05.272 --> 05:07.406
It's okay.

05:07.508 --> 05:10.242
